SasadaKopi Roastery is the right place to enjoy high quality coffee. This cafe has a modern atmosphere with a vintage touch which makes it comfortable for all occasions, whether for work or just relaxing. SasadaKopi Roastery also offers a variety of delicious pastries and light bites to perfectly complement each cup.
